Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:23.69,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you, Lilly?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:27.13,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Cabbage's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:29.39,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing a wrestling tour,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:33.09,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can take it easy here\Nand think about what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:40.72,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I possibly do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:43.73,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Prostitution is all I've ever done...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:45.32,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What can a useless woman like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:50.41,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,...ever possibly do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:54.71,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't like you, Lilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:00:58.50,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.67,0:01:02.48,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard to make\Nit this far on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:08.40,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you have our help too.\NSo don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.68,0:01:20.14,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you and Noboru go\Nto such lengths for other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:24.90,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's what Anchan taught us.\N--Anchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:32.03,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,The one the MPs shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:40.01,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,We're filled with his\Nteachings right in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:44.38,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,We're indebted to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:51.82,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could Turtle be, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:55.14,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was going\Nto drop by this morning...
