Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:19.52,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0410,,Man, I didn't know he\Nlived in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:19.79,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,"Marutaka Rice Shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:24.66,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He really kept it a secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:29.55,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:32.05,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Turtle! I know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:34.91,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.46,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...! Turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.86,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--Noboru!\N--Turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:47.37,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Noboru?!\NSay something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.47,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Lilly! I'll take him to a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:56.84,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh? A cold?\N--Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:04:00.59,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He had difficulty breathing\Ndue to his high fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.81,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,but the antipyretic I gave him\Nshould help him feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:09.79,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be safe, we'll keep him\Nhere a few days for observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:11.31,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:14.81,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:18.88,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really just a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.14,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:25.54,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't anything\Nelse wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:30.31,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! Don't worry us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:32.88,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.49,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Something good to eat\Nwould perk me back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:40.74,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:46.70,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll peel an apple for you now.\NYou should be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:48.10,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.20,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:56.49,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, a small\Nclinic like this won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:05:00.70,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll need to try a bigger hospital\Nto find out anything for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.72,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah! It's good!\N--Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:13.79,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Lilly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:17.70,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you thought about\Nwhat you're gonna do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:25.75,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Brooding over it won't solve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:31.25,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't so bad when I think\Nof it as making a fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:38.66,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to earn a living\Nall this time. All on my own, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.79,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,So things will work out for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:52.17,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That secret stash of money\Nyou kept from that military guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:54.05,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you planning to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:59.31,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have anything big in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:03.92,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought it'd be\Nnice to own a small shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:10.26,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,My own castle where I can survive\Nwithout having to rely on men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:14.33,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a meager little dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:17.45,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:24.06,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,How much would it cost\Nto make your little dream come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:33.10,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly! You shouldn’t\Nask questions like that, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.83,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's the matter, Mario?\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:49.09,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been looking glum since we left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:54.48,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it's really\Njust a cold Turtle has?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.44,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's what the doctor said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:04.37,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting at, Mario?!\NIs something wrong with Noboru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:11.34,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He's... an atomic bomb orphan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:18.08,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean... he's having\Naftereffects from the blast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:24.73,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, We need to get\Nhim checked at a big hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:32.44,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I don't have the money\Nor connections to take him to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.66,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Lilly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:43.84,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I possibly do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:47.49,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:54.64,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything for Turtle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:58.62,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.06,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one cares about his\Nfriends as much as he does.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:10.81,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Turtle is so nice because he bears a\Nmore painful past than anyone else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:16.17,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mario was filled with frustration{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:22.95,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that he could only stand transfixed\Nwith fear of this invisible threat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:30.89,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Mr. Maeda!\NIt's time to check your temperature!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:41.20,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Lilly...!\NWhat brings you over so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:44.24,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to take Noboru\Nto a big hospital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:46.83,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Then come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:57.70,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we at an\NAmerican army base, Lilly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.82,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were going to a hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:04.15,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario.\NAmerica made the atomic bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:06.67,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:11.25,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,America also had the most advanced\Nmedical expertise in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:16.86,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no better place\Nto get Noboru's illness looked at.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:21.99,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0410,,"Cafe Milonga"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.91,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,There's 100,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:27.00,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That's everything I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.58,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I offer it and myself as collateral!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:37.36,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Use me as you see fit! You don't\Neven have to pay me for my work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:42.05,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Just, please! Lend me some money!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.58,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:51.20,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,300,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:10:00.21,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I only lend up to 3000 yen\Nat a time. No exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:13.11,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please allow me to use this\N100,000 to start a business like yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:16.01,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You, a 1% lender?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:19.43,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lend 100,000 to start,\Nthat's 1,000 yen a day in interest,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.67,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,30,000 in a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:25.55,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,A month later, that 130,000 yen\Nwill become 169,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:30.60,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to choose\Nany line of work you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.75,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:37.07,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I've no reason to stop you.\NDo as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:40.03,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:41.71,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:48.14,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:53.20,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want you to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:05.67,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, why are we at a public bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:09.44,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly, now. No dawdling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:19.18,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely there's nothing wrong\Nwith scrubbing an old man's back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:32.58,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0410,,So, can you talk to the\Nhospital to take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.64,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Lilly. Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.96,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,They used to serve under my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:44.49,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You can do something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:48.02,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta my sight, geisha girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:54.48,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That old fart's no longer in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:57.96,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer the superior's girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:07.06,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0410,,Or, what? You'll play with\Nme like you did with the man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:10.39,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0410,,Then why don't you join\Nme in my bed later tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:12.60,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--The hell I will!\N--Lilly
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.28,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! These guys have to pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:20.21,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless. There's no\Npoint trying to talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:22.93,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Lilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:25.64,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, Mario! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:35.37,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,We can figure out another way, Lilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.52,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.70,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Mario Minakami, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.32,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:54.42,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.19,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,See if this will shake up your memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:07.46,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... from that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.16,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:22.30,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm the Jeffrey you knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.57,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:29.33,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0410,,That left...\NMan, that really worked me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:32.69,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, about that doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.80,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I can pull some strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:37.75,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:41.34,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he'll ask them\Nto take a look at Noboru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.44,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:45.35,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--We appreciate it!\N--Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:48.04,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,But... there's one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:52.33,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0410,,Mario. I wanna box\Nwith you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:55.31,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Lilly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:14:00.33,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He just said he wants\Nto box with me, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:04.12,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... That's his one condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:10.41,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. But it has to be right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:17.05,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario... Are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:37.68,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.43,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that Jap's got some moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.91,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please! Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:46.25,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:57.59,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:01.05,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Jeffrey. It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:03.40,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Sarge! It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.05,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:09.09,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:13.15,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0410,,Jeffrey, do you really\Nwant to beat up a cripple?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:20.20,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0410,,Sir, what are you saying?! He's a\Ngood boxer! He knocked me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:45.24,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0410,,The hospital will take a look\Nat him tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.23,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0410,,--Really?!\N--Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:51.40,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! They're going\Nto take a look at Noboru tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:52.70,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:56.44,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:58.37,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:02.21,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:17.65,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Jeffrey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:19.04,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:27.72,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,So that somebody is worth that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:36.28,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0410,,Someone who is so precious\Nthat you would box with that fist?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:40.84,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Jeffrey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:48.77,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,As the saying goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:53.75,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Borrow with a smile, repay with a scowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:58.70,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,People are quick to offer\Ngratitude when borrowing money,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:03.67,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,but glare at you like the devil\Nas soon as they have to pay it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:11.81,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you scrub my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:20.65,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I was given those scars\Nshortly after I became a moneylender.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:23.18,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,And this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.25,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,...and these ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:32.60,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,All the other scars during my\Nten years as a moneylender
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:36.84,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,were given to me by people\Nwho borrowed money from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:48.89,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lend to the wrong person,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:54.92,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll lose not only your precious\N100,000, but your life as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:58.89,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you still be a 1% lender anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:03.99,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:10.95,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With his scars, Mr. Sugi showed\NTurtle the viciousness of his profession{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:16.34,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and that there are beats in the\Nworld that repay kindness with hate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:21.35,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being a 1% moneylender is\Nnot for regular, honest people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:26.46,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In his heart, Turtle felt\Nthat there was no better job{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:29.41,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for someone as risk-taking as him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:36.26,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How many decorations would be\Ncarved into his own minuscule body?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:48.16,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You said earlier that you\Noffer yourself as collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:51.15,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you serious when you said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:54.37,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:19:00.35,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I do have one request for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:08.08,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to get the person living\Nhere to repay the money he owes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:09.15,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:12.65,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can do it, I'll agree to\Nyour 300,000 yen proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.05,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:22.43,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you're not careful, you could\Nend up with the same scars as mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.67,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you still do it anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:32.62,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:36.41,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Have 300,000 yen ready when I get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:42.06,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:44.94,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you need so much money for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.46,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Women? Your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:51.42,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:56.01,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's for my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:19:59.57,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:03.42,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He was long gone when we\Nchecked him this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:08.84,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What does Noboru think\Nhe's doing in his condition?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:10.98,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.12,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's search for him, Mario!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:20.17,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Igarashi! Are you home, Mr. Igarashi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:25.35,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the noise! Try selling\Nme anything and you'll get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:29.00,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:31.45,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a messenger for Mr. Sugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:32.59,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:36.70,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that old geezer moneylender?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:39.24,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--C'mon! Hurry it up!\N--Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:50.40,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Lilly... This isn't for just you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:55.14,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also my chance\Nto take a step forward...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.18,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Standing around won't solve anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.71,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You gotta use your body\Nand mind to move forward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:10.08,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no point in being\Nborn if you can never be happy!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:16.46,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anchan's teachings\Npushed Turtle forward...{\i0}
